{"tid":1686516,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"回應要求林鄭辭任港大校監 楊潤雄：十年前曾作檢討故不需再討論","createTime":"2019-11-01T07:31:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T02:05:24.000Z","uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4c5b33ad4b6cfb95152d589cde53699cb8780fc1","tid":1686516,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T07:31:30.000Z","msg":"楊潤雄就教育局發禁蒙面法通告至幼稚園致歉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】教育局上月初要求全港中學，提交戴口罩、罷課或參與校外人鏈的人數，局長楊潤雄在立法會教育事務委員會上表示，局方鑑於近期情況改善，並沒有再主動詢問每間學校的狀況。<br />\n<br />\n被問到局方早前將有關禁蒙面法的通告發送至幼稚園，楊潤雄指由於時間倉促，承認幼稚園學生並沒有戴口罩到街上所衍生的風險，有就事件向幼稚園校長道歉。<br />\n<br />\n多名建制派議員亦關注有學生參與近期暴力衝突。<br />\n<br />\n被問到是否需要成立危機小組處理，楊潤雄指現時局方每天有就事件進行討論。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">對於港大畢業生議會通過要求行政長官林鄭月娥辭任校監，楊潤雄指十年前曾作檢討，暫時看不到要再討論。</span>"},{"pid":"7286812d01afc01a7976074e49067af1c8f5ecf3","tid":1686516,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T07:31:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=368360&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D368360%26refer%3D&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvD44BXU%2FO%2BPkTPvsbUsuc1I%3D&h=c2d5b823\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D368360%26refer%3D&h=c673d2b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=368360&amp;refer=</a>"},{"pid":"61b828c48f9e9b46199b48ef4a31e24a225e2723","tid":1686516,"uid":173207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T07:39:11.000Z","msg":"香港政府的檢討就係唔檢討 死雞撐飯蓋<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00dd98ca87f5f19e38f0c789cb2d859e1629